    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Multidisciplinary, nonprofit organizations comprised of professionals, generally architects and planners, and volunteers working to improve social and economic conditions in a neighborhood or community.</Note_Text>
